# Copy this file to .env.local and add your Google Gemini API key.
# Get a FREE key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey (no billing required).
#
# The free tier (gemini-2.5-flash) reads PDFs and is plenty for personal use:
# ~10 requests/minute, ~250 requests/day. A 100+ page cookbook imports in one go.
#
# NOTE: Vite exposes any variable prefixed with VITE_ to the browser bundle,
# so this key is visible to anyone using the deployed app. For a free key the
# risk is low (worst case: someone uses up your free quota — rotate the key to
# fix it). For a hardened deployment, proxy the call through a serverless
# function instead of calling the API directly from the browser. See README.md.
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key-here
